{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d6a872fcc9","title":"周恩来对科学院哲学社会科学部两次谈话中有关清查“五·一六”的内容","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d0c8741919","index":0,"year":1969,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"d6a872fcc9"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"a0d5508956","name":"清查五·一六","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d54f35267f","type":"title","text":"周恩来对科学院哲学社会科学部两次谈话中有关清查“五·一六”的内容","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9"},{"id":"95fd7268c3","type":"paragraph","text":"6月28日和7月31日两次讲话摘录：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9"},{"id":"9517280786","type":"paragraph","text":"“五·一六”是利用1967年发表《5.16通知》搞起来的，他们抓的很快，主席抓的更快。姚文元9月份发表文章点“五·一六”是反动组织，主席8月份就抓住了，主席看的准……“五·一六”串连，小报上都透露了，主席很快就发现了，矛头不对。原来后台就是王、关、戚。起头，我们想分化他们，把戚本禹分出来，实际上他们是一伙。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9"},{"id":"33aa744511","type":"paragraph","text":"（1969年6月28日接见学部宣传队和大联委时的讲话）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9"},{"id":"a90c9cba6d","type":"paragraph","text":"要先从提高思想、落实政策方面入手。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9"},{"id":"a628d1cf5e","type":"paragraph","text":"你们要把“五·一六”、大批判、清队、整党搞好。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9"},{"id":"d198765ccd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1969年7月31日接见学部宣传队和大联委时的讲话）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9"}],"page":{"id":"38d9ba77e6","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d6a872fcc9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}